                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1517925680837-ryerson-purchasing-card--p-card-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1517925680837-ryerson-purchasing-card--p-card-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1517925680837-ryerson-purchasing-card--p-card-" aria-expanded="false">
                            Ryerson Purchasing Card (P-Card)
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1517925680837-ryerson-purchasing-card--p-card-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1517925680837-ryerson-purchasing-card--p-card-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1517925680837 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="274fde24-3e08-4425-910e-e6169f063f75" >

    <p>If accepted by the vendor, paying with a P-Card is the preferred method for low-dollar purchases less than $5,000 CAD, although some <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/financial-services/purchasing-payment/paying-vendors/#p-card-ssi-exceptions">exceptions</a> apply.</p> 
<p>To apply for a P-Card, visit the <a href="/content/ryerson/financial-services/purchasing-payment/purchasing-card.html">Purchasing Card page</a>.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#274fde24-3e08-4425-910e-e6169f063f75");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1517925681377-electronic-funds-transfer--eft-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1517925681377-electronic-funds-transfer--eft-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1517925681377-electronic-funds-transfer--eft-" aria-expanded="false">
                            Electronic funds transfer (EFT)
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1517925681377-electronic-funds-transfer--eft-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1517925681377-electronic-funds-transfer--eft-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1517925681377 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="7e5679b5-1905-4fb2-bfa2-3042fc4df4b4" >

    <p>EFTs are recommended for vendors wishing to receive payments directly into their Canadian bank account. Currently, we do not offer EFT payment for non-Canadian bank account holders.</p> 
<p>Vendors who prefer this method can request an EFT Registration Form by contacting <a href="mailto:invoices@ryerson.ca">invoices@ryerson.ca</a>. Once completed, submit the form with a void cheque or bank letter via the Financial Services dropbox at 1 Dundas West, 9th floor.</p> 
<p>Information collected by Ryerson remains confidential and will not be released under any circumstances, unless required by law.</p>
    





</div>
